    <text xml:lang="ta" corresp="#Ed" type="edition">
        <body>
            <div xml:id="KT400-kilavi">
                <p type="edition">viṉaimuṟṟi vanta talaimakaṉ ṟērppākaṉait talaiyaḷittatu. </p>


                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">HE, who comes after having completed [his] work,
                    showing politeness to the charioteer. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="KT400">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> cēyāṟu cellā māyi ṉiṭariṉṟu</l>
                    <l> kaḷaikalaṅ kāmam peruntōṭ keṉṟu</l>
                    <l> naṉṟupurin teṇṇiya maṉattai yāki</l>
                    <l> murampukaṇ ṇuṭaiya vēkik karampaip</l>
                    <l> putuvaḻip paṭutta matiyuṭai valavō</l>
                    <l> yiṉṟu tantaṉai tērō</l>
                    <l> nōyuḻan tuṟaiviyai nalka lāṉē.</l>


                </lg>

                <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <l> As one with a mind , who considered [and] desired what is good:</l>
                    <l rend="indent"> “if we don't go the way through the distance without
                        impediment,</l>
                    <l rend="indent"> we won't alleviate the desire for [her with] big shoulders”,</l>
                    <l> you charioteer with a mind that effects new paths</l>
                    <l rend="indent"> in the wasteland, setting of to break into mounds of gravel,</l>
                    <l> have you given [just] the chariot today?</l>
                    <l> With this you are granting [also] her,</l>
                    <l rend="indent6"> who constantly endures pain .</l>


                </lg>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
